[[File:聚三牌.png|thumb]]'''聚三牌'''（{{vie|hn=|qn=Tổ tôm}}），在[[後黎朝|黎]]末[[阮朝|阮]]初時[[范廷琥|范廷琥]]的《日用常谈》就有記載<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nomfoundation.org/common/vshow.php?detail=2098|title=游 戲 門 - Du hí|language=vi|publisher=Vietnamese Nôm Preservation Foundation|author=范廷琥|date=|accessdate=2015-02-08|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208075104/http://nomfoundation.org/common/vshow.php?detail=2098|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是流傳於[[越南|越南]]北部的[[葉子戲|葉子戲]]<ref name="Bí ẩn bộ bài tổ tôm hay mối quan hệ Nhật – Việt chưa có lời giải"></ref>。

==牌具==
一到九的序數牌，[[花色|花色]]有萬、索、文，每門各四張，另有類似[[水滸牌|水滸牌]]的三元牌各四張，共一百二十張<ref name="Culture and Customs of Vietnam">{{cite book |author=Mark W. McLeod、Nguyen Thi Dieu|title=《Culture and Customs of Vietnam》 |date=2008-11-04 |publisher=Greenwood Press|location=美國 |language=en |isbn=9780313304859}}</ref>，為何牌面為穿著[[和服|日本傳統服飾]]的人物？專家也表示不解<ref name="Bí ẩn bộ bài tổ tôm hay mối quan hệ Nhật – Việt chưa có lời giải">{{Cite news|url=http://www.138.com.vn/choi-bai-an-tien/archives/bi-an-bo-bai-to-tom-hay-moi-quan-he-nhat-viet-chua-co-loi-giai/|title=Bí ẩn bộ bài tổ tôm hay mối quan hệ Nhật – Việt chưa có lời giải|language=vi|publisher=138 và world cup 2014|author=|date=2013-08-24|accessdate=2013-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224104153/http://www.138.com.vn/choi-bai-an-tien/archives/bi-an-bo-bai-to-tom-hay-moi-quan-he-nhat-viet-chua-co-loi-giai/|archive-date=2013-12-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
